def conversion_2400(fecha):
    if fecha[11:13] != '24':
        return pd.to_datetime(fecha, format='%d/%m/%Y %H:%M')

    fecha = fecha[0:11] + '00:' + fecha[14:]
    return pd.to_datetime(fecha, format='%d/%m/%Y %H:%M') + dt.timedelta(days=1)

# CALCULO FORMAL DE LOS LIMITES SUPERIOR E INFERIOR

Pot_Instalada = pd.Series([25.0, 25.0, 25.0], index=['TD1', 'TD2', 'TD3'])
POT_INSTALADA = Pot_Instalada.sum()

q75, q25 = TD1['TD1_MVA'].quantile(0.75), TD1['TD1_MVA'].quantile(0.25)
IQR = q75 - q25
bigote = 3 * IQR
lim_sup, lim_inf = q75 + bigote, q25 - bigote
if lim_inf < 0 :
    lim_inf = 0.0

    
# PODRIA USAR DIRECTAMENTE COMO LIMITES
lim_sup = Pot_Instalada.TD1 * 1.20
lim_inf = 0
In [11]:
# IDENTIFICAR ATIPICOS
TD1_atipicos = TD1[(TD1['TD1_MVA'] < lim_inf) | (TD1['TD1_MVA'] > lim_sup)]
print('Atipicos identificados: %d' % len(TD1_atipicos))


# REMOVER ATIPICOS
TD1_sin_atipicos = TD1[(TD1['TD1_MVA'] >= lim_inf) & (TD1['TD1_MVA'] <= lim_sup)]
print('TD1_MVA sin Atipicos: %d' % len(TD1_sin_atipicos))

# CALCULO FORMAL DE LOS LIMITES SUPERIOR E INFERIOR

q75, q25 = TD2['TD2_MVA'].quantile(0.75), TD2['TD2_MVA'].quantile(0.25)
IQR = q75 - q25
bigote = 3 * IQR
lim_sup, lim_inf = q75 + bigote, q25 - bigote
if lim_inf < 0 :
    lim_inf = 0.0

    
# PODRIA USAR DIRECTAMENTE COMO LIMITES
lim_sup = Pot_Instalada.TD2 * 1.20
lim_inf = 0
In [27]:
# IDENTIFICAR ATIPICOS
TD2_atipicos = TD2[(TD2['TD2_MVA'] < lim_inf) | (TD2['TD2_MVA'] > lim_sup)]
print('Atipicos identificados: %d' % len(TD2_atipicos))


# REMOVER ATIPICOS
TD2_sin_atipicos = TD2[(TD2['TD2_MVA'] >= lim_inf) & (TD2['TD2_MVA'] <= lim_sup)]
print('TD2_MVA sin Atipicos: %d' % len(TD2_sin_atipicos))

# CALCULO FORMAL DE LOS LIMITES SUPERIOR E INFERIOR


q75, q25 = TD3['TD3_MVA'].quantile(0.75), TD3['TD3_MVA'].quantile(0.25)
IQR = q75 - q25
bigote = 3 * IQR
lim_sup, lim_inf = q75 + bigote, q25 - bigote
if lim_inf < 0 :
    lim_inf = 0.0

    
# PODRIA USAR DIRECTAMENTE COMO LIMITES
lim_sup = Pot_Instalada.TD3 * 1.20
lim_inf = 0
In [36]:
# IDENTIFICAR ATIPICOS
TD3_atipicos = TD3[(TD3['TD3_MVA'] < lim_inf) | (TD3['TD3_MVA'] > lim_sup)]
print('Atipicos identificados: %d' % len(TD3_atipicos))


# REMOVER ATIPICOS
TD3_sin_atipicos = TD3[(TD3['TD3_MVA'] >= lim_inf) & (TD3['TD3_MVA'] <= lim_sup)]
print('TD3_MVA sin Atipicos: %d' % len(TD3_sin_atipicos))

def Grafica_xmin(pi, pf):
    plt.style.use('fivethirtyeight')
    
    #y = datos.loc[anio:anio, 'MVA'].resample('D').max()
    #x = y.index

    x = gg['TD1_MVA']
    y = gg['TD2_MVA']
    z = gg['TD3_MVA']
    s = gg['Suma']
    t = x.index 
    
    fig = plt.figure()
    fig, grafico = plt.subplots(figsize=(30, 5))

    grafico.plot(t, y, lw=1, label='TD2', marker='o', color='y')

    grafico.legend()  # Add a legend.
    
    grafico.grid(visible='True', which='major', axis='both', color='black', alpha=1, linewidth=0.5)

pf = anio_fin + '-12-31'

dias = pd.date_range(start=pi, end=pf, freq='D')
for dia in dias:

# Obtengo los Valores Maximos x MES  ---- No puedo utilizar resample('D') porque me da los valores Maximos para todas las columnas
# y yo necesito los valores MVA para los cuales Suma es maxima en el MES

#anios = ['2011', '2012', '2013', '2014', '2015', '2016', '2017', '2018', '2019', '2020']

Pot_max_xmes = pd.DataFrame(columns = ['TD1_MVA', 'TD2_MVA', 'TD3_MVA', 'Suma'])

anio_ini = '2011'
anio_fin = '2020'
pi = anio_ini + '-01-01'
pf = anio_fin + '-12-31'

meses = pd.date_range(start=pi, end=pf, freq='M')
for mes in meses:
    mes = mes.strftime('%Y/%m')
    if Trafos.loc[mes, :].empty :
        pass
    else:
        ind = Trafos.loc[mes, 'Suma'].idxmax()
        Pot_max_xmes.loc[ind] = Trafos.loc[ind, ['TD1_MVA', 'TD2_MVA', 'TD3_MVA', 'Suma']]

# Grafica del Pico Maximo Potencia Aparente x DIA

def Grafica_Pot_Max_xMes(pi, pf):
    plt.style.use('fivethirtyeight')
        
    TD1 = Pot_max_xmes.loc[pi:pf, 'TD1_MVA']
    TD2 = Pot_max_xmes.loc[pi:pf, 'TD2_MVA']
    TD3 = Pot_max_xmes.loc[pi:pf, 'TD3_MVA']
    Suma = Pot_max_xmes.loc[pi:pf, 'Suma']
    tiempo = TD1.index 
    
    fig = plt.figure()
    fig, grafico = plt.subplots(figsize=(30, 5))
    
    #grafico.plot(x, y, lw=1, label='Potencia Aparente', marker='o')
    grafico.plot(tiempo, TD1, lw=1, label='TD1', marker='o', color='g')
    grafico.plot(tiempo, TD2, lw=1, label='TD2', marker='o', color='y')
    grafico.plot(tiempo, TD3, lw=1, label='TD3', marker='o', color='b')
    grafico.plot(tiempo, Suma, lw=2, label='TD1+TD2+TD3', marker='o', color='k')
    
    grafico.set_xlabel('[ Meses ]')  # Add an x-label to the axes.
    grafico.set_ylabel('[ MVA ]')  # Add a y-label to the axes.
    grafico.set_title("POTENCIA APARENTE DIARIA " + pi +' '+pf)  # Add a title to the axes.
    grafico.legend()  # Add a legend.
    #grafico.annotate('Pico Max', xy=(01-31 14:45, 75), xytext=(01-31 15:00, 75), arrowprops=dict(facecolor='black', shrink=0.05)
    #grafico.grid()
    
    #fig.savefig("Serie_Anual_xDia_"+anio+".png")
